      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S offers a masterclass in mid-engine balance and mechanical feedback. At its heart is a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus, delivering a linear power band and a visceral soundtrack. The 6-speed manual transaxle provides crisp gear engagement, while the chassis\u2014utilizing a rigid subframe and optimized MacPherson strut geometry\u2014ensures exceptional lateral acceleration and precise steering telemetry. This example has been maintained with an emphasis on drivetrain health, showing consistent compression across all cylinders and a dry undercarriage. Ideal for the driver seeking a pure, analog connection to the tarmac without the complexity of modern electronic interference.",
